Rubicite leggings and helm, Staff of the Observers, Runed Mithril Bracers X2, Reed Belt, Grotesque mask, Bloodstained Tunic, Platinum Jasper rings X2, Platinum Ruby Veil, Gold Wisdom? Earrings X2, 3500pp, and much, MUCH more.<BR>
<BR>
For those of you looking to get great items, at low cost, i recommend the "Nosowfoyou Tactics" and rip off a guild here and there.  And for those of you who don't like what i have done, let you rest in your jelousy as i sit happily with my 2 Runed Mithril Bracers. :)<BR>
<BR>
Good Luck</font></td></tr></table>
