<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>DO NOT attempt to kill the King unless you and your groupmates have cleaned the junks and break the spawn, must be at least 40+ and buffed with either regen or another other hp buff, cuz the king hits hard, 100dmg per hit easy. and for its annoying pet, root it, or have it feared, it will suicide once the king is dead. and DO NOT use battle song, it will drive him frenzy and your bard will die fast if you don't co-op. <BR>
Our group held the king room for almost a day =) A wiz, an enchanter, cleric, pally and two big tanks, everyone got their bracelets and bp.  BTW don't use lotto, it can be cracked. Best way to do it is to give whoever stay the longest in the group and need the item most.<BR>
